      "role": "user",
      "content": "1-2%? that's basically zero. so you're saying there isn't even a new breakthrough coming? like, medically speaking, is there any chance of a cure being developed for people who are already treatment-resistant, or is the science just stuck? i just need to know if i'm fighting for something that doesn't exist.",
